description: True North Energy Corp. acquires, explores, develops, and produces oil and gas properties in the United States. The company also provides shoes through its stores located in Europe, Japan, and the United States, as well as through online. True North Energy Corp. was formerly known as Ameriprint International Ltd. and changed its name to True North Energy Corp. in January 2006. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Spring, Texas.
